@startuml ResumeForge_ActivityDiagram

!theme vibrant
skinparam backgroundColor #f8f9fa
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #e9ecef
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #343a40
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #ffc107
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #343a40
skinparam ArrowColor #007bff
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

title Automated Resume Generation System - Activity Diagram

|User|
start
:Enter Personal Data & Resume Details;

|System Backend|
:Validate Input Data;

if (Data Valid?) then (No)
  |User|
  :Prompt for Missing/Invalid Info;
  :Update Information;
  |System Backend|
  :Re-validate Data;
endif

|System Backend|
:ML Domain Classification\n(DistilBERT categorizes user industry);
:Generate Prompt\n(Structuring inputs for AI);

|Machine Learning Model|
:Process Prompts & Generate Content;

|System Backend|
:Structure Content\n(Organize into resume sections);
:Generate Output Document\n(PDF / DOCX formatting);

|User|
:Preview and Download Resume;

stop

@enduml
